reviews.review_text: this rocks oregon trail mix love it !!!

Wow!!! The SOTM is easily in the top three ever. Jerry's final solo is ragin'. The rest of the second set features Huey Lewis and they seem to have a grand time playing lots of blues.
5 for the SOTM

Great Show I'm glad someone posted this! I recorded it on a HiFi Stereo VCR (not standard equipment then) set on a timer from my hotel room at the Eugene Hilton, not far from the venue. I don't see too many copies of the Oregon Trail Mix clip (which was played over the PA system at Autzen Stadium before the show) or the post-show interview.

oh, and that high pitch noise is from the original capture of the broadcast...it is what it is!

...enjoy!
VCR transfer—sweet This sounds pretty damn good datmike. Thanks for capturing this FM goodness. I always enjoy leaning about the rigs that recorded the shows I listen to.
